{{Infobox television | show_name = Legends & Lies | image = Legends_&_Lies_title_card.jpg | image_size = 250 | image_alt = | caption = | genre = [[Documentary]]/[[Historical drama]] | creator = | writer = | director = Kevin Hershberger | presenter = [[Bill O'Reilly (political commentator)|Bill O'Reilly]] (Seasons 1-2), Brian Kilmeade (Season 3)<ref>{{cite web|title=SUNDAY: 'Legends & Lies' Returns With a Riveting Look at The Civil War|url=http://insider.foxnews.com/2018/03/23/legends-lies-civil-war-premieres-sunday-preview-season-3-docu-series|website=Fox News|accessdate=25 March 2018}}</ref> | narrated = [[Dermot Mulroney]] | opentheme = | composer = | country = United States | language = English | num_seasons = 3 | num_episodes = 34 | list_episodes = | executive_producer = Bill O'Reilly | producer = | cinematography = | camera = | runtime = 60 minutes | company = | distributor = | channel = [[Fox News]] | picture_format = [[1080i]] | audio_format = [[Dolby Digital]] Stereo | first_aired = {{start date|2015|4|12|mf=yes}} | last_aired = Present | related = | website = http://www.foxnews.com/shows/l-and-l | production_website = }} '''''Legends & Lies''''' is an [[Americans|American]] [[television series]], shown on [[Fox News Channel]]. Its primary [[executive producer]] is [[Bill O'Reilly (political commentator)|Bill O'Reilly]].
The show's premise is the presentation of the history of notable figures in history in [[documentary]] style, debunking certain elements of their historical stories that have entered [[popular culture|pop culture]] [[mythology]]. The series features dramatizations of parts of the subjects' lives and exploits, as well as explanatory segments by historians and experts, and often O'Reilly himself.
The show premiered in April 2015. Its normal broadcast schedule is on Saturday and Sunday nights.
Each season of the series also features an accompanying book, co-authored by David Fisher and O'Reilly.<ref>{{cite book|isbn=978-1627795074|first1=David|last1=Fisher|first2=Bill|last2=O'Reilly|title=Legends & Lies: The Real West|location=New York|publisher=[[Henry Holt and Company]]|date=April 2015}}</ref>
The most recent season (season 3) had its finale on June 10, 2018.
